{"tid":2100677,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國擬起訴反華學者智庫？ 外交部：惡意誹謗應受追究","createTime":"2020-07-09T08:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T09:13:33.000Z","uid":51665,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c840e0832e01de053bb95c0acea9ec67d54cd00e","tid":2100677,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2691091/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E5%8F%8D%E8%8F%AF%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB%EF%BC%9F%20%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97%E6%87%89%E5%8F%97%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2691091%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25BA%25AB%25EF%25BC%259F%2520%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25AA%25B9%25E8%25AC%2597%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmmyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=4b17dca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2691091/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E5%8F%8D%E8%8F%AF%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB%EF%BC%9F%20%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97%E6%87%89%E5%8F%97%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6</a><br />\n內地《環球時報》昨日引述消息報道，中方有關部門正考慮起訴新疆問題專家鄭國恩（Adrian Zenz）、澳洲戰略政策研究所（ASPI）等學者和智庫，指稱其「炮製涉華謊言」，要造究其造謠誹謗的法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅今日（9日）表示，任何惡意誹謗行為都受到譴責和追究，有關報道如果屬實，並不感意外。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅表示，鄭國恩和澳洲戰略政策研究所「一貫炮製涉華謊言」，誹謗中國，又稱他們發表的有關涉華言論「被證明是謊言和虛假信息」。他稱「多行不義必自斃」，奉勸有關方面盡快回頭是岸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他又說，留意到鄭國恩接受自由亞洲電台的採訪，質問「如果鄭國恩沒有撒謊造謠，他心虛什麼？」強調任何惡意誹謗行為都應受到譴責和追究，這是常識。<br />\n<br />\n鄭國恩：當局想他噤聲 起訴反令維吾爾人受關注<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台昨引述鄭國恩稱，看到了中方計劃起訴他的消息，表示這是當局試圖讓他噤聲的手段之一，但認為如果中方真的起訴，反而可能會提升國際社會對維吾爾人的關注，「這是件好事」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》昨報道，近年鄭國恩和ASPI頻頻在涉疆、涉新冠肺炎疫情等領域發表涉華報告，對中國抹黑攻擊。其中ASPI被指散播「中國威脅論」。文章稱他們表面上是學者、智庫，實際上是可笑的「牽線木偶」，受美澳反華勢力的操縱，編造涉華謊言，進行不實指控。<br />\n<br />\n一定要告到你班仆街裙甩褲甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f423be7194e9906d3e65afa54f7dce2e9c03ad1a","tid":2100677,"uid":183758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"真係癲撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人哋唔將你視為敵國都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7498a91903bc0ae1a52da07b8066131603c5947c","tid":2100677,"uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫善意誹謗"},{"pid":"34e7b312d7c57146d16016aa607e8bd5d68538a5","tid":2100677,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"只要唔去中共聯邦國家就安全"},{"pid":"76fc11d473397699a8ab135b0e53ebf9182b8c7d","tid":2100677,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:04:36.000Z","msg":"如果蒼井堅沒有撒謊造謠，牠心虛什麼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f512ee295e2f7600f20bd5bd96ab38992a51bfc","tid":2100677,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"國安法有用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5aa4fe77ba9dd42f6fb72aa1762298b9015217","tid":2100677,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"即係香港d大行報告都唔可以唱淡中資股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b918f888b61afa04c8670b0e72afc4234252e6a","tid":2100677,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:10:01.000Z","msg":"又要譴責誹謗又話如屬實並不意外，即係點啊？？彈出彈入玩晒啦"},{"pid":"